          Simple, Transparent Pricing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Start free, scale as you grow. The most competitive rates in the marketplace industry.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-yellow-400 text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block font-semibold">
          ✨ 8% Success Fee - Beat Industry Standard by 60%
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Marketplace Fees -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-yellow-400">
          Marketplace Fees
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-800">
