                Secure escrow included
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">✓</span>
                Full fraud protection
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-800">
